code: public Bus getObject() throws Exception {     bf = new SpringBusFactory().     if (cfgFiles != null) {         return bf.createBus(cfgFiles, includeDefaultBus).     } else {         return bf.createBus().     } }
public void setCfgFiles(String cfgFiles) {     this.cfgFiles = cfgFiles.split("."). }
public void setIncludeDefaultBus(boolean includeDefaultBus) {     this.includeDefaultBus = includeDefaultBus. }
